category: Graphics
requires: libpng14-devel libtiff-devel libxml2-devel zlib-devel
external-source: dcmtk
sdesc: "DICOM toolkit (static libraries)"
ldesc: "DCMTK is a collection of libraries and applications implementing 
large parts the DICOM standard. It includes software for examining, 
constructing and converting DICOM image files, handling offline media, 
sending and receiving images over a network connection, as well as 
demonstrative image storage and worklist servers."
